## Content Calendar Creation

Build a comprehensive content calendar:

- [ ] 1. Content Pillars: Define 3-5 content themes based on {{objectives}}
- [ ] 2. Platform Mix: Select platforms based on {{target_audience}} and objectives
- [ ] 3. Frequency: Set posting frequency per platform
- [ ] 4. Content Types: Plan mix of content types (posts, stories, reels, blogs)
- [ ] 5. Calendar: Map content to specific dates, noting key events and campaigns

## Inputs
- Client: {{client_name}}
- Platforms: {{platforms}}
- Frequency: {{frequency}}
- Objectives: {{objectives}}
- Target: {{target_audience}}
